PR is open: [jdx/mise#10876](https://github.com/jdx/mise/pull/10876)

Implemented Rust install reconciliation so `mise install` no longer skips an already-installed Rust toolchain when configured `components` or `targets` are missing. Array form in `mise.toml` is now documented and explicitly tested for both `components` and `targets`.

Verified with:

```sh
cargo test rust_options
cargo test rustup_component
mise run test:e2e e2e/core/test_rust_components_reconcile
```

